cs.DC, cs.OS, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper primarily focuses on the architecture and operating systems of disaggregated data centers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also proposes additional OS abstractions and interfaces for disaggregation, which falls under the category of Operating Systems (cs.OS). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges in providing applications with this additional functionality, which falls under the category of Architecture (cs.AR), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
